title: MNF Recap; Doug Baldwin Stops By
itunes:title: MNF Recap; Doug Baldwin Stops By
description:
A room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Colleen Wolfe & Gregg Rosenthal recap all the latest news from around the NFL including Andrew Luck sitting out week 2, David Johnson’s wrist surgery and when Thomas Rawls is expected to return. The heroes give their opinions on 0-1 teams to worry about and are also joined by Seattle Seahawks Wide Receiver Doug Baldwin.
